# Grobles - Technology Startup Portfolio

This is an Astro-powered portfolio website for Grobles, a technology startup focused on:
- Mobile app development
- Web application development  
- Digital marketing
- Technology consultancy
- Custom tech solutions

## Project Structure

## Core Configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) - Astro configuration with MDX, sitemap, and Tailwind CSS
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript config with path aliases (`@/*` â†’ `./src/*`)

## Source Structure
- [src/consts.ts](mdc:src/consts.ts) - Global constants (SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION)
- [src/content.config.ts](mdc:src/content.config.ts) - Content collections schema for blog posts
- [src/styles/global.css](mdc:src/styles/global.css) - Global styles with custom DaisyUI theme

### Key Directories
- `src/components/` - Reusable Astro components
- `src/layouts/` - Page layouts (BlogPost.astro, Page.astro)
- `src/pages/` - File-based routing pages
- `src/content/blog/` - Blog/news posts and case studies
- `src/assets/` - Static assets and images

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Astro 5.12.8
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4.1.11 + DaisyUI 5.0.50
- **Content**: MDX support with content collections
- **Icons**: Lucide Astro
- **Fonts**: Poppins (Google Fonts)

## Custom Theme
Uses a custom DaisyUI theme called "grobles" with green-tinted color scheme that reflects the startup's brand identity, defined in global.css.